fields.headline: John Kerry in London and 65th anniversary of the founding of North Korea: the best news pictures of the day
fields.bodyText: Sweet tweet! One of the funniest pictures of the day has been spotted on Patrick Stewart's twitter feed where he revealed to his followers that he'd married singer Sunny Ozell. Congratulations you two!
